<div id="country3" class="tabcontent">
<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">

<h2>Fatal Document Tracking</h2><hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen will capture fatal document of death patient in the hospital.
<br /><hr /><br />

<img src="images/mis_fataldocumenttracking.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />

<p>
<span class="title">Service No: </span><br />
User can write patient service number, it can't remain 
<br />
<span class="title">HIN: </span> <br />
Based on service number user can select HIN Number, it can't remain blank. 
<br />
<span class="title">Ad No: </span> 
<br />Based on service number and HIN Number user can select Admission and discharge number, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Date of Death & Remarks:</span> 
    <br />Based on Admission and discharge number patient date of death details will come, it can't remain blank. And user can write remarks.
<br />
    <span class="title">Postmortem & Remarks:</span> 
    <br />User can select the postmortem details from the given list, it contains 1) Held and 2) Not Held, and user can write remarks.
<br />
    <span class="title">Date of Postmortem Received & Remarks:</span> 
    <br />User can select the date of postmortem received details, and user can write remarks.
<br />
    <span class="title">Documents H/O spl concerned date & Remarks:</span> 
    <br />User can select the document Head of specialist concerned date details, and user can write remarks.
<br />
    <span class="title">Received from spl with opinion and date & Remarks:</span> 
    <br />User can select the received from specialist opinion date details, and user can write remarks.
<br />
    <span class="title">Completion of documents by ward master and date & Remarks:</span> 
    <br />User can select the completion of documents by ward master details, and user can write remarks.
    <br />
    <span class="title">Signature of MO i/c & Remarks:</span> 
    <br />User can select the signature of medical officer in charge date details, and user can write remarks.
    <br />
    <span class="title">HOD perusal on (date) & Remarks:</span> 
    <br />User can select the head of department perusal on date details, and user can write remarks.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Date of submission of stats by ward master & Remarks:</span> 
    <br />User can select the date of submission stats details by ward master, and user can write remarks.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Date of submission for remarks of commandant & Remarks:</span> 
    <br />User can select the date of submission for remarks of commandant details, and user can write remarks.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Date of dispatch to senior advisor pathology for perusal & Remarks</span> 
    <br />User can select the date of dispatch to senior advisor pathology perusal details, and user can write remarks.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Date of dispatch to senior advisor perusal & Remarks:</span> 
    <br />User can select the date of dispatch to senior advisor perusal details, and user can write remarks.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Date of dispatch to concerned command for perusal & Remarks:</span> 
    <br />User can select the date of dispatch to concerned commandant for perusal details, and user can write remarks.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Save (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on save button user can save the data. 
    
    
</p>

